item.title: Compiler?
item.dc:creator: @Porsche_911_Freak Porsche 911 Freak
item.description:
@Porsche_911_Freak wrote:

Right-click your compiler and click edit, is this in there anywhere?

@echo off title servername "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk#.#.#_##\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk#.#.#_##\bin\java.exe" server pause

If it isn’t you probably need to add it.

(the number symbols are where you enter your version of java development kit)
